channel.title: Pemp Cane 474 *Added some media *Videos soon *Daily updates
channel.description:
[b][size=18pt]I am making this for a friend and also going to release once it's done.[/size][/b]
[b]Features:[/b] - Combat - Lunar's - Prayer - Smithing ( Smelting ) - Smithing ( Equipment making ) - Fishing - Cooking - Firemaking - Clipping ( Npc ) - Clipping ( Player Following ) - Daily Task - Dual Arena - Warriors Guild ( Defenders ) - Barrows - Real RuneScape GodWars - [b]More to come...[/b]
[b]Meda:[/b] [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/impezo.png[/img]
[img]http://i48.tinypic.com/4sg17n.png[/img]
[img]http://i46.tinypic.com/2egfhw9.png[/img]
- [b]More to come...[/b]
[b]Update logs:[/b] [code]*April 1st 2013 - Download Normal PI all dupes fixed. - Started clipping - Started Fishing - Completed Fishing & fixed a few bugs for fishing - Started Firemaking
*April 2nd 2013 - Started smelting - Started smithing ( equipment making ) - Completed smelting ( known bugs- you keep smelting if you walk away ) - Added 474 npc's ( you need to add on client & I commeted it out in source ) - Started Cooking - Completed cooking ( buring rate is off ) - Started on lunar's - Started on Prayer - Completed Prayer - Made Client a Webclient - Completed cliped player following - Completed Npc clipping
*April 3rd 2013 - Started Dail Task ( Well thought of it, will work on it later going to bed :D )
*April 4th 2013 - Started Warriors Guild - Completed Warriors Guild - Started GodWars ( real rs godwars, but maybe not npc attacking each other )[/code]
[b]Credits:[/b] - Any tuts used - PI - Me - Strucker ( helping me a lilbit on smelting )
